  "instructions": [
    "Cut the guava, mango, banana, and strawberries into bite-sized pieces",
    "Cut the grapefruit and pomegranate into segments",
    "Grill the pineapple slices until slightly charred, about 2-3 minutes per side",
    "Peel and chop the mango, banana, and strawberries",
    "Mix together the grilled pineapple, chopped mango, banana, and strawberries in a large bowl",
    "Drizzle the lime juice over the fruit mixture and sprinkle with smoked salt",
    "Sprinkle the coconut flakes and honey over the fruit mixture and toss to combine",
    "Sprinkle the cilantro over the top of the fruit mixture and serve",
    "Heat the avocado oil in a small pan over medium heat",
    "Add the red pepper flakes, crushed red pepper, smoked paprika, and garlic powder to the pan and stir to combine",
    "Pour the spicy oil over the fruit mixture and toss to combine"
  ],
